682,"uid":33727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T15:37:33.000Z","msg":"大<span style=\"color: red;\">阪</span><br />\n<br />\n要睇你咩時間去, 撞正紅葉同櫻花期, 機票同住宿都好貴"},{"pid":"eecaba73b24e49066f85c6a42cbf9790183c5f49","tid":427682,"uid":2161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T03:26:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大<span style=\"color: red;\">阪</span><br />\n<br />\n要睇你咩時間去, 撞正紅葉同櫻花期, 機票同住宿都好貴</blockquote><br />\n我岩岩買11月中 hx連稅1200一個 住宿都係1300蚊晚6個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd0c5736d749da7b9981a5b849d3ceb9e7ad6d77","tid":427682,"uid":32294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T09:28:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>大<span style=\"color: red;\">阪</span><br />\n<br />\n要睇你咩時間去, 撞正紅葉同櫻花期, 機票同住宿都好貴</blockquote><br />\n我岩岩買11月中 hx連稅1200一個 住宿都係1300蚊晚6個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你住邊道？"},{"pid":"eeecceb2c5d6eade7826c55f12398ca48c44d783","tid":427682,"uid":11787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T09:31:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>大<span style=\"color: red;\">阪</span><br />\n<br />\n要睇你咩時間去, 撞正紅葉同櫻花期, 機票同住宿都好貴</blockquote><br />\n我岩岩買11月中 hx連稅1200一個 住宿都係1300蚊晚6個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n千2咁撚抵 D時間西唔西先"},{"pid":"111928b700a2b798456f0d6d67a5840787f2775f","tid":427682,"uid":44814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T09:31:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>大<span style=\"color: red;\">阪</span><br />\n<br />\n要睇你咩時間去, 撞正紅葉同櫻花期, 機票同住宿都好貴</blockquote><br />\n我岩岩買11月中 hx連稅1200一個 住宿都係1300蚊晚6個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/